      <span class="panel-kicker">Limitations</span>
      <h2 id="limitations-title">What a responsible evaluation can and cannot prove</h2>
      <p>
        A one-week market result can be affected by noise, unusual events, and the chosen asset universe. It is a real
        outcome, but it is not by itself proof of persistent investment skill.
